    "curator_notes": "This series spans three separate Spotify artists: 'Sternenschweif' (main series, episodes 1-75), 'Sternenfohlen' (spinoff series about the foal Wolke, episodes 1-42), and 'Sternenschweif - Sternchen' (shorter stories for younger children, episodes 1-4). The main Sternenschweif series has duplicate releases for episodes 1-3 (older 2007-2008 versions vs newer 2025 versions); the newer releases are preferred. The 'Einhornmärchen' album is a standalone compilation of unicorn fairy tales and not part of the numbered episode sequence. Episode numbering uses 'Teil', 'Band', or 'Folge' prefixes interchangeably."
  },
